---
title: Blackened Barramundi & Mango Salsa with Scallion Rice & Roasted Green Beans
description: Mango salsa is our favorite way to feel warm weather vibes all year round. It’s sweet, juicy, and tangy, making it the perfect complement to crispy, spiced barramundi. On the side, there’s roasted green beans and fluffy rice mixed with scallions and tangy lime zest. No matter the temperature, one bite of this delicious dish will make everything feel a whole lot sunnier.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/blackened-barramundi-pineapple-salsa-d5d98aff.jpg
